description: This Chainlink VRF top 9% rating Cooter purrs with a rating of 77, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 154, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Box for North, 8 for East, Box for South, and 1 for West. Cooter has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/90772-48412-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
